data.description: Welcome to Wyndham Ranch! This home offers  a spacious living room, an open kitchen which features an island with seating as well as a dining area. On the second floor you’re greeted with a built in work area as well as the primary bedroom with ensuite and 2 additional bedrooms. Conveniently located,  close to shopping, schools, and all the amenities in Spanaway!
